00:00:12.677 --> 00:00:16.746
What are you making?
Nemchenu Muddalu (Rice Laddu)

00:00:23.349 --> 00:00:25.508
Ingredients required to make Nemchenu Muddalu (Rice Laddu)

00:00:25.743 --> 00:00:31.428
Rice, Cashews, Raisins, Sugar, Cardamom, Ghee

00:00:50.362 --> 00:01:00.000
Take a pan and roast a cup of rice

00:01:16.456 --> 00:01:21.715
Take the roasted rice aside

00:01:26.447 --> 00:01:36.438
Grind the roasted rice into a powder.
Also, grind 1 1/2 cup of sugar into a powder (separately)

00:02:18.136 --> 00:02:24.170
Take a pan and heat a generous amount of ghee

00:02:26.744 --> 00:02:33.820
Mix the sugar powder and the rice powder

00:02:44.970 --> 00:02:49.852
Add some cardamom powder to it

00:02:58.665 --> 00:03:06.665
Add the hot ghee to the mixed powder

00:03:18.701 --> 00:03:26.926
Meanwhile, take a pan and heat some oil/ghee
to fry some raisins

00:03:30.316 --> 00:03:34.222
Take the fried raisins aside

00:03:41.127 --> 00:03:45.819
Fry some cashews as well

00:03:58.611 --> 00:04:03.968
Add the required amount of hot ghee 
to the rice &amp; sugar powder to make a nice dough like mixture

00:04:07.440 --> 00:04:13.316
Make small round balls(laddu) with the dough

00:04:18.833 --> 00:04:24.362
Garnish with some fried cashews

